{"id":362,"date":"2021-12-23T08:48:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-23T06:48:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=362"},"modified":"2022-10-18T15:18:06","modified_gmt":"2022-10-18T12:18:06","slug":"10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/","title":{"rendered":"10 Best Practices for Corporate Cloud Banking"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Corporate cloud banking adoption rates have continued to soar among digital payments companies every year since the early 2000s.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And as <a href=\"https:\/\/userguiding.com\/blog\/digital-transformation-trends\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">today\u2019s digital transformation<\/a> continues to drive the demand for disruptive solutions, businesses in the payments industry have no option but to adapt to emerging technologies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Although adopting corporate cloud banking has many benefits for an enterprise, there\u2019s a need to exercise caution from the get-go.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite the internal pressure to speed things up, the IT teams need to understand everything related to the cloud. <strong>Adopting cloud computing<\/strong> calls for much more than a basic understanding of what it is and how it works.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The successful adoption of cloud computing in a business requires laser-like focus, a cultural change, and a detailed blueprint developed with input collected from the entire company.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A forgotten software installed deep inside the IT infrastructure, or a single missed step can cause expensive and time-intensive outages, disruptions, and delays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" area-label=\"ez-toc-toggle-icon-1\"><label for=\"item-673d663aad2c2\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;direction:ltr;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input  type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item-673d663aad2c2\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#best-cloud-practices-for-enhanced-business-transformation\" title=\"Best Cloud Practices for Enhanced Business Transformation\">Best Cloud Practices for Enhanced Business Transformation<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#1-assign-a-cloud-steward-for-the-enterprise\" title=\"1. Assign a Cloud Steward for the Enterprise\">1. Assign a Cloud Steward for the Enterprise<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#2-schedule-a-cloud-vaccination-program-for-the-enterprise\" title=\"2. Schedule a Cloud Vaccination Program for the Enterprise\">2. Schedule a Cloud Vaccination Program for the Enterprise<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#3-define-its-goals-and-how-it-can-lead-to-business-transformation\" title=\"3. Define Its Goals and How It Can Lead to Business Transformation\">3. Define Its Goals and How It Can Lead to Business Transformation<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#4-evaluate-the-complexity-of-the-digital-systems\" title=\"4. Evaluate the Complexity of the Digital Systems\">4. Evaluate the Complexity of the Digital Systems<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#5-implement-a-cloud-based-as-a-service-business-model\" title=\"5. Implement a Cloud-Based-as-a Service Business Model\">5. Implement a Cloud-Based-as-a Service Business Model<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#6-determine-which-enterprise-assets-need-to-move\" title=\"6. Determine Which Enterprise Assets Need to Move\">6. Determine Which Enterprise Assets Need to Move<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#7-implement-a-dual-migration-approach\" title=\"7. Implement a Dual Migration Approach\">7. Implement a Dual Migration Approach<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#8-create-an-all-inclusive-corporate-cloud-banking-strategy\" title=\"8. Create an All-inclusive Corporate Cloud Banking Strategy\">8. Create an All-inclusive Corporate Cloud Banking Strategy<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#9-promote-ongoing-optimization-and-improvement\" title=\"9. Promote Ongoing Optimization and Improvement\">9. Promote Ongoing Optimization and Improvement<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/10-best-practices-for-corporate-cloud-banking\/#10-use-the-digital-payments-system-to-build-a-minimum-viable-cloud\" title=\"10. Use the Digital Payments System to Build a Minimum Viable Cloud\">10. Use the Digital Payments System to Build a Minimum Viable Cloud<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"best-cloud-practices-for-enhanced-business-transformation\"><\/span><strong>Best Cloud Practices for Enhanced Business Transformation<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sticking to a prescriptive approach when implementing a cloud solution in a <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/corporate-cloud-banking-and-strategic-growth\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"130\">digital payments<\/a> firm helps reduce risks, fast-track time to value, and streamline business transformation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best practices for implementing cloud computing in the payments industry include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-assign-a-cloud-steward-for-the-enterprise\"><\/span><strong>1. Assign a Cloud Steward for the Enterprise<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A cloud steward refers to the person who will lead the cloud initiative meant to transform the business.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The steward will handle all aspects related to implementing cloud computing in the digital payments systems, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Planning<br>\u2022 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.toolbox.com\/tech\/cloud\/articles\/what-is-cloud-migration\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cloud migration<\/a><br>\u2022 All ongoing cloud operations, e.g., optimization, security, and governance<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on the management structure in the enterprise, they may also handle contract negotiations with cloud service providers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An ideal steward will possess both IT and business expertise.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Assign-a-Cloud-Steward-for-the-Enterprise.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1054\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Assign-a-Cloud-Steward-for-the-Enterprise.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Assign-a-Cloud-Steward-for-the-Enterprise-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Assign-a-Cloud-Steward-for-the-Enterprise-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-schedule-a-cloud-vaccination-program-for-the-enterprise\"><\/span><strong>2. Schedule a Cloud Vaccination Program for the Enterprise<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It shouldn\u2019t come as a surprise to learn that not everyone working in the payments industry is open to the idea of shifting to <a href=\"https:\/\/gozazoo.com\/blog\/zazoo-modern-banking-solution-confirmed-to-be-launching-this-fall\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">corporate cloud banking<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore, you should expect to encounter some resistance even in your own organization. The reality is that conscious resisters and blockers are present in all companies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, it\u2019s possible to prevent this by planning an early intervention. Try to bring all the key stakeholders in one room early on to immunize the company against resisters.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-define-its-goals-and-how-it-can-lead-to-business-transformation\"><\/span><strong>3. Define Its Goals and How It Can Lead to Business Transformation<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>During the sit-down mentioned above, try to ensure that all stakeholders are reading from the script regarding shifting to corporate cloud banking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, they should have an idea of what will happen once the migration is complete. It\u2019s why goal setting is a step that you can\u2019t afford to skip.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Approach goal setting as a formal process or as a documented business case. Potential goals can include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 A baseline for the existing IT setup<br>\u2022 Key performance indicators to use in measuring the success of the migration process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-evaluate-the-complexity-of-the-digital-systems\"><\/span><strong>4. Evaluate the Complexity of the Digital Systems<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The primary consideration when attempting to determine the complexity of an application is its connections.<br>Take your time to map the application dependencies to understand all the other servers and applications it communicates with.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Determine whether the communication is unidirectional or bidirectional.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check for dependencies and multi-tier dependencies between different elements of the firm and the payments industry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-implement-a-cloud-based-as-a-service-business-model\"><\/span><strong>5. Implement a Cloud-Based-as-a Service Business Model<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It will make sense for the cloud steward to start by leveraging and implementing business software applications as a service to drive business transformation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The cloud will assist in paving the way for an efficient <a href=\"https:\/\/searchcloudcomputing.techtarget.com\/definition\/Software-as-a-Service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">as-a-service model<\/a>. Adopting an as-a-service model allows the company to use cloud resources based on its current needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can scale these resources as its needs continue to evolve.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6-determine-which-enterprise-assets-need-to-move\"><\/span><strong>6. Determine Which Enterprise Assets Need to Move<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The best practices for <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/corporate-cloud-banking-and-strategic-growth\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"130\">corporate cloud banking<\/a> require that you create a cloud migration strategy with more than an overview of your current IT setup.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You need to take stock of every aspect of your digital payments system, including available applications, hardware, services, and data in the system.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An excellent starting point will involve creating a detailed list of available assets and their interdependencies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7-implement-a-dual-migration-approach\"><\/span><strong>7. Implement a Dual Migration Approach<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Experts in the payments industry recommend shifting the most basic applications first and following this up with the complex ones. It\u2019s the general rule of thumb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting with complex applications can create a headache for the company and those overseeing the migration and implementation processes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mobile workstreams offer the greatest flexibility and are easier to move. Greater planning and coordination are needed for complex apps.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/3.-Define-Its-Goals-and-How-It-Can-Lead-to-Business-Transformation.jpg\" alt=\"cloud banking\" class=\"wp-image-421\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/3.-Define-Its-Goals-and-How-It-Can-Lead-to-Business-Transformation.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/3.-Define-Its-Goals-and-How-It-Can-Lead-to-Business-Transformation-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/3.-Define-Its-Goals-and-How-It-Can-Lead-to-Business-Transformation-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8-create-an-all-inclusive-corporate-cloud-banking-strategy\"><\/span><strong>8. Create an All-inclusive Corporate Cloud Banking Strategy<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating a <a href=\"https:\/\/synoptek.com\/business-infrastructure-and-systems-solutions\/cloud-advancement\/cloud-strategy-and-planning\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">robust adoption strategy<\/a> for corporate cloud banking can aid in faster implementation and allow for business transformation with fewer risks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Developing a comprehensive cloud adoption strategy will require you to consider all the areas that will likely get adopted by adoption, e.g.,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Your business<br>\u2022 The company personnel<br>\u2022 Existing governance structure and framework<br>\u2022 The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripwire.com\/state-of-security\/security-data-protection\/cloud\/efficient-cloud-security-strategy-experts-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">company security<\/a> framework<br>\u2022 Day-to-day operations<br>\u2022 Platform considerations<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9-promote-ongoing-optimization-and-improvement\"><\/span><strong>9. Promote Ongoing Optimization and Improvement<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You shouldn\u2019t perceive the processes involved in cloud adoption as a one-time effort. There\u2019s a need to develop economic processes and modelling and routinely revisit them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this, you should include metrics and processes from the business line, technology, and finance. For example, you can consider chargeback, value measurements, and budgets.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The focus here is to create an approach that allows for a continuous process and mentions the steps needed for further improvement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"10-use-the-digital-payments-system-to-build-a-minimum-viable-cloud\"><\/span><strong>10. Use the Digital Payments System to Build a Minimum Viable Cloud<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Of the ten practices mentioned here, the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.cloudtp.com\/minimum-viable-cloud\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">minimum viable cloud (MVC)<\/a> is among the most important and based on the minimum viable product concept.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It serves as the starting point for the first production of any application you\u2019ll rely on during the business transformation. It\u2019s a platform you will need to iterate and improve on going forward.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From this point, you must think of the cloud as a piece of software linked that supports your digital payments system.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Corporate cloud banking adoption rates have continued to soar among digital payments companies every year since the early 2000s. And as tod